               <p>Q. When did you loose your pipe - A. Near eight o'clock at night.</p>
               <p>Q. Where was it fixed - A. To the washhouse, I saw the prisoner in the passage, I opened the door, he appeared loaded; I saw in the passage a bit of pipe; I overtook him, he fell down, he got up and run away from me, through Dove-court, he threw the pipe away, I overtook him, and brought him home.</p>
               <p>
            
